column1: LBNL_001,,,"Identify each entity that is a zone, and either has a directly associated property or is indirectly connected to a property via a RoomDomainSpace through a chain of connections.",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
LBNL_001,,,"For each zone (target), what are the related non-writable property labels and ALC and MPC endpoint references?",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>

LBNL_001,,,"For each Zone that either has a Property directly or has a RoomDomainSpace reached by two connected steps and a contains relationship leading to a Property, what is the label of that Property and what are the external reference alc endpoint and mpc endpoint when writable is False?",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
# Indirect case via two connected steps to a RoomDomainSpace that contains a property
# Only external references where writable is false

LBNL_001,,,"Which properties associated with building zones (including those linked through room domain spaces and chained connections) are read-only, and what are their labels together with the alc and mpc endpoints in their external references?",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
# Traverse from zone to any linked property via various relationships (direct or indirect)
# Restrict to property instances (observable or actuatable)
# Property is read‑only: either no writable flag or explicitly false

LBNL_001,,,List the labels of all non-writable properties for zones and show the corresponding alc endpoint and mpc database endpoint for each.,lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
LBNL_001,,,What alc and mpc endpoints are defined for the read-only properties of each zone?,lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
# Read‑only: either no writable flag or explicitly false
# ALC and MPC endpoint names if present
LBNL_001,,,How can I find the alc and mpc endpoints for zone properties that aren't editable?,lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>

LBNL_002,,,"Identify each entity that is an AHU, and either has a directly associated property or is indirectly connected to a property via a connectable.",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>

LBNL_002,,,"For each Air Handling Unit (AHU) whose label includes 'RTU', what are the related non-writable property labels and ALC and MPC endpoint references?",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>

LBNL_002,,,"For each air handling unit whose label contains rtu, identify any connectable element it contains that observes or has property a property, or any property it has directly, and for each property give its label along with the ALC endpoint and the MPC database name from its external reference",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
# Air handling units (RTUs) whose label contains 'rtu'
# Properties directly on the AHU (treated as its own element)
# The element may observe or have a property

LBNL_002,,,"For RTU air handling units, what are the property names and their associated ALC and MPC endpoints defined in the external references",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>

LBNL_002,,,"Which RTU units expose properties with external endpoints, and what are the property labels along with those ALC and MPC endpoint addresses",lbl/cborg-coder,,"PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
